Key Match Events: Renat Dadachov scored for Azerbaijan in the 82nd minute
Alexander Isak scored twice for Sweden in the 65th and 71st minutes
Viktor Gyökeres scored for Sweden in the 80th minute via penalty
Post-Match Reflections: Erik ten Hag praised Sweden’s performance and the team’s ability to maintain focus despite the late goals
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match ended 1-3 in favor of Sweden
Sweden secured 3 points in the 2024-25 UEFA Nations League
Azerbaijan remains without a point in the group stage
Others: Tofik Bakhramov Stadium hosted the match
Referees were Balazs Berke, Balazs Berke (Assistant), and Attila Kovacs (Fourth)
